<div style="font-size: 325%;">3.</div>
</td>
<td><a href="/wiki/File:Monty-CurlyPicksGoatB.svg" class="image" title="Monty-CurlyPicksGoatB.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/09/Monty-CurlyPicksGoatB.svg/163px-Monty-CurlyPicksGoatB.svg.png" width="163" height="125" border="0" /></a></td>
