<td><a href="/wiki/File:Monty-SwitchfromGoatB.svg" class="image" title="Monty-SwitchfromGoatB.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f6/Monty-SwitchfromGoatB.svg/194px-Monty-SwitchfromGoatB.svg.png" width="194" height="125" border="0" /></a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
